<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
      <h1>AMBICIÓN</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="col-lg-2">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2>We are a coffee roasting startup in Paris. Our goal is to bring you amazing coffees for fair prices. Try our latest specialty coffee, we are sure you will love it.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-2">
      </div>
      <br>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="cta-button">
        I want a free sample NOW
      </button>
    </div> 
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" style="margin-top:2em;">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <%= image_tag('coffee_beans.jpg', :id => "beans-image") %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-top:2em;">
      <div class="col-lg-2">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2>Yes, this is what amazing coffee looks like. It tastes like dark chocolate, peach or sometimes even champagne. Let us make you a better cup of coffee.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-2">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container" style="margin-top:2em;border-top: 3px solid #2ABB9B;">
  <div class="row" id="descriptor-row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <i class="fa fa-leaf fa-5x" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#26A65B;margin-top:0.5em;"></i>
        <br>
        <p>It starts with the selection of rare and amazing coffees from farms/producers all over the world</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <i class="fa fa-fire fa-5x" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#F89406;margin-top:0.5em;"></i>
        <br>
        <p>We then roast, curate, select and assemble the most incredible single origins and blends</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <i class="fa fa-dropbox fa-5x" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#CA6924;margin-top:0.5em;"></i>
        <br>
        <p>Our deliciously fresh roasted coffee is delivered to your door every week/month</p>
      </div>
      <br>
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <p style="font-style:italic;margin-top:2em;">* We take 7% of our revenues and donate them to Fundación Alto Quiel.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>